      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with regular driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable; the leather seats show some minor creasing but no tears or heavy wear. All electronic features and climate controls are fully functional. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has a documented service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that presents well and drives great.",
