      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving straight-six retains excellent compression and is paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under lateral load. The M-Variable differential provides predictable lockup for corner-exit traction. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including cooling system components and rod bearings\u2014are in robust health. A purist\u2019s spec with functional aerodynamics and a balanced chassis dialed for the twisties.",
